d evaluating Blueprints, entry to 101 level. Implementing ideas and improvements in the manufacturing process The capacity of fast learning of new products and processes and implementation in existing product lines Excellent project management software skills Ability to travel 30% of the time Ability to work outside Experience in the oil and gas industry preferred Authorized to work in the United States Valid Driver\u2019s license Bilingual preferred: English - Russian at the professional level Fluent or native Russian at the professional level Minimum 2 years of experience project engineering, project management Ability to work independently Excellent computer skills NOTE: This job description is not intended to be all-inclusive. The employee may perform other related duties as negotiated to meet the ongoing needs of the organization. Work from River West, Chicago office, traveling Job Type: Full-time * Job Type: Full-time Pay: $40,000.00 - $52,000.00 per year Schedule: Monday to Friday Supplemental Pay: Bonus Pay Experience: project engineering, project management: 2 years (Preferred) Language: Russian (Preferred) Work authorization: United States (Required) Required travel: 25% (Preferred) Company's website: https://www.ezblockchain.net/ Work Remotely: Yes ", 
